my dad was totally

167
00:08:33.330 --> 00:08:36.260
helpless in the kitchen.
we went out every night.

168
00:08:36.260 --> 00:08:37.670
Over dinner. he would tell me

169
00:08:37.670 --> 00:08:39.610
