172
00:08:44.550 --> 00:08:47.850
He'd say. "And what
happened to those girls?"

173
00:08:47.850 --> 00:08:50.390
Well. those girls got
married out of high school.

174
00:08:50.390 --> 00:08:52.210
they put their husbands through college

175
00:08:52.210 --> 00:08:53.650
