177
00:08:57.440 --> 00:08:59.343
Sometimes the husband would die.

178
00:09:00.490 --> 00:09:02.800
Sometimes.

179
00:09:02.800 --> 00:09:04.620
the husband would get bored

180
00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:07.790
